Package org.apache.ruples.mutable.table

package org.apache.ruples.mutable.table
This package contains MuTableKV implementation.

The classes in this package are:

  • KeyValue - KeyValue Tuple implementation.
  • MuTableRow - MuTableRow List of KeyValue items.
  • MuTableKV - MuTableKV List of MuTableRow items.
https://github.com/abritoh/ruples

    org.apache.ruples.mutable

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    KeyValue<KEY,VALUE>
    Represents a generic key-value pair where the key and value types are parameterized.
    MuTableKV
    The MuTableKV class is a JAXB-serializable representation of a table-like structure where each row contains a list of key-value pairs.
    MuTableRow
    The MuTableRow class is a JAXB-serializable representation of a row structure this row contains a list of key-value pairs.
